{
  "texts": [
    "Optimized Libraries.",
    "Our experiments with the parlayNN library [98] (Fig. 17) indicate the importance of such work.",
    "For instance, the parlayNN HCNNG_Opt implementation was scalable to 1B datasets, whereas the non-optimized version could not scale beyond 25GB.",
    "Other methods could benefit from such optimizations to scale to large datasets, and further efforts are needed by the community to adopt and support libraries such as parlayNN.",
    "Recommendations."
  ]
}